[ブルー f=01]「Yeah, that's right. He's a pathetic loser who was defeated by me, had his woman taken away by me, and couldn't do anything to fight back.」[k]
[テオ f=09]「Damn...!」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「So, what are you doing here? Are you planning to defeat me?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「...!」[k]
[textoff]

*_revenge_ask
@question title="Are you up for the challenge of Blue?"
[if exp='! tf.result']
	[texton]
	[テオ f=06]「No, it's nothing...」[k]
	I can't beat Blue right now. I've decided to turn back.[k]
	[textoff]
	@eval exp='game.party.escape(true)'
	[eventoff]
[endif]

[texton w=0]
[テオ f=06]「Yes. Blue, I came here to defeat you.」[k]
[ブルー f=08]「...What?」[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=08
[texton w=1]
Blue's eyes narrowed. He slowly stood up and faced me.[k]
[テオ f=05]「Blue! I challenge you all. It's a duel!」[k]
@fg c=ブルー e=帯刀 f=02
[ブルー f=02]「...You've got some nerve. I beat you up so badly last time, but it looks like you haven't learned your lesson yet.」[k]
[ブルー f=15]「All right. I'll take you on. This time, I'll beat you all half to death. You'll never dare to defy me again!」[k]
[マックス f=12]「Eek!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...!」[k]
It's finally time for the rematch with Blue...! It's okay, I can win this time. We'll definitely win![k]
[textoff]

; 決闘用の網を表示
@anime_duel_net visible=true

[texton]
∗whoosh∗[k]
A transparent barrier appears around everyone in the room. It's a sign that the Duel God has approved our duel.[k]
At this point, there's no turning back. Our only future lies in defeating Blue.[k]
[エリック f=01]「You really never learn, do you?」[k]
[ミレディ v=vm132 f=05]「What, another duel? That's so annoying!」[k]
[サンドラ v=vn003 f=05]「Come on... Don't challenge Blue to a duel... There's no way you can beat him.」[k]
Blue's allies gather around, to fight with him. We must be careful of them as well.[k]
Especially Miredy. How to counter her anti-magic will be the key to this battle.[k]
We should be careful of the new elf woman too. Her power is unknown. I don't know what she might do.[k]
[ブルー f=01]「Let's get started, [テオ]!」[k]
[テオ f=07]「Let's go, Blue!」[k]
It's finally time...! We'll definitely win and set Riselle free.[k]
[textoff]
@clf

; ブルーのパーティーと戦闘
@eval exp='game.curTeam = o.ブルー・ファミリア'
@addevent name=戦闘 num=12
@eval exp='m.ミレディ.btcmd.add(o.アンチマジック)'
@eval exp='m.ミレディ.speed = 99'
@monster pos=1 name=ミレディ
@monster pos=3 name=キャプテン
@monster pos=5 name=エリック
@monster pos=9 name=ブルー
@monster pos=11 name=サンドラ
@eval exp='game.inDuelBattle = true'
@callbattle bgm=boss
@anime_duel_net visible=false
@anime_duel_sign visible=false

; 敗北
@jump target=*_revenge_lose cond='game.getBattleResult() == "lose"'

; 勝利
@eval exp='game.party.minimumRecovery(true)'
@delevent map=ブルーのアジト１Ｆ num=2
@delevent map=ブルーのアジト２Ｆ num=1
@addevent map=ブルーのアジト１Ｆ num=3
@jump target=*_revenge_win

*revenge_5_again
; ブルーに改めて戦いを挑みに行く場合

[texton w=0]
[ブルー f=05]「It's you again. What are you doing here?」[k]
[textoff]
@jump target=*_revenge_ask

*_revenge_lose
@saveoff
@fg c=ブルー e=戦闘 f=15
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=09]「Damn...!」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「Don't you understand my power? You'll never be able to defeat me.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
It's frustrating, but I can't argue with that... Blue is strong, after all. Too strong. It was a mistake to even try to beat a guy like that in the first place...![k]
[ブルー f=02]「Well, this time, [テオ], it's your turn.」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What...?」[k]
[ブルー f=02]「This time, I'll add you to my party. And you'll work under me until you die. Just like before.」[k]
[テオ f=09]「Ugh...!」[k]
His request to the Dual God was granted. A magical collar briefly formed around my neck.[k]
[ブルー f=02]「You will be my slave forever. That's the fate you were born with. Do you understand, [テオ]?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w2
[texton]
And so, I spent the rest of my meaningless life exploited as Blue's subordinate...[k]
[textoff]
@jump storage="script.ks" target=*_event_game_over
*_revenge_win

@fg c=ブルー e=戦闘 f=10
[texton]
[ブルー f=10]「Damn it!」[k]
[テオ f=13]「We did it...! We beat Blue...!」[k]
I finally did it...! I finally beat Blue.[k]
[ブルー f=10]「Ugh...」[k]
[textoff]
@clf
@se f=dosa
@quake time=200 hmax=10 vmax=5
@wq
@w05
[texton]
Blue collapsed onto the floor![k]
[ブルー e=通常 f=10]「Damn it... [テオ]... You...!」[k]
Blue is unable to move due to the power of the Duel God. Lying on the ground, he bitterly complains about his defeat.[k]
But no matter what Blue says, I am the victor this time.[k]
You lost to me. You were certainly strong, but you were by no means invincible.[k]
[テオ f=05]「I won, Blue. Now, give me back Riselle.」[k]
[ブルー f=13]「...Heh.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What? What's wrong?」[k]
[ブルー f=13]「I mean... You've been... Desperately trying... For that woman... All this time... It's funny...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「What are you talking about?!」[k]
[ブルー f=13]「Nothing... Go and see... That woman... Beyond that door...」[k]
Blue looks toward the rear door, indicating Riselle's location.[k]
[テオ f=06]「...」[k]
What are you trying to say, Blue? We won, but that feels like a taunt.[k]
[マリア v=va160 f=07]「Who cares about him?! More importantly, hurry up and find Riselle...!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Y-you're right.」[k]
We decided to go look for Riselle.[k]
[textoff]
@eval exp='o.リーゼル.pregnantCount = 1'
@eval exp='o.リーゼル.strip.blue = "ボテ腹"'
[eventoff]
;◇イベント06・アジトの奥でリーゼル発見
*revenge_6

; ブルーの屋敷の奥でリーゼル発見
@saveon
[texton w=1]
[テオ f=11]「Riselle!」[k]
I opened the door to the room where I thought Riselle was. Then...[k]
[リーゼル e=寝室のキャミソール f=05]「...!」[k]
[マリア v=va161 f=51]「Riselle?!」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl389 f=05]「Captain... Maria...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「Riselle...!」[k]
[textoff]
@out

@bg f=event68 p0=01
@mu f=calm
[texton w=2]
Riselle was there, in a small room.[k]
She sat on the bed and looked at me calmly.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl390 f=13]「It's been a while... Captain... Maria...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What...?!」[k]
[マリア v=va162 f=51]「R-Riselle...!」[k]
Both Maria and I were shocked to see Riselle's current condition.[k]
Riselle's belly had grown so much![k]
[マリア v=va163]「Ah... you... your stomach...!」[k]
@bg f=event68 p0=02
[リーゼル v=vl391]「Yes, it's probably Blue's child...」[k]
[マリア v=va164]「Blue's... child...?!」[k]
[テオ]「...」[k]
She spoke as if it were nothing. She seemed calm, showing no signs of worry.[k]
Riselle, bearing a child of that hateful man...[k]
It's Blue's fault. He probably just came inside her repeatedly without thinking. And this is the result.[k]
What an irresponsible man...! How could he toy with people so badly...[k]
[マリア v=va165]「What are you saying?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl392]「Umm. It's okay to have a baby. I want to have one too.」[k]
Saying that, Riselle stroked her large belly lovingly. Her eyes had already become those of a mother.[k]
The woman I once loved is now about to give birth to a child fathered by another man...[k]
[リーゼル v=vl393]「Captain... it's been a while...」[k]
[テオ]「Ah-ahhh...」[k]
@bg f=event68 p0=04
[リーゼル v=vl394]「I'm glad you came to help me... But I don't feel the same way about you any more...」[k]
[テオ]「I-I understand...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl395]「I'm sorry... Even though you helped me...」[k]
[テオ]「No... I'm the one who caused you pain... I'm sorry.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl396]「Umm...」[k]
[テオ]「...」[k]
[リーゼル]「...」[k]
Silence fell between the two of them. He could feel that a huge gap had formed between them.[k]
[テオ]「What will you do now?」[k]
@bg f=event68 p0=02
[リーゼル v=vl397]「First, I want to give birth to this child and raise it...」[k]
[テオ]「I see...」[k]
@bg f=event68 p0=03
[リーゼル v=vl398]「You know, Captain, you might not believe this, but I like Blue. I've fallen in love with him.」[k]
[テオ]「Well...」[k]
I knew it all along, but hearing it from her directly was painful.[k]
[リーゼル v=vl399]「I want to stay by Blue's side... I'm happy that everyone helped me, but I don't want to leave here...」[k]
@bg f=event68 p0=04
[リーゼル v=vl400]「...I understand. No matter how much I care about Blue, there's no guarantee that Blue will care about me... Blue is popular with women...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl401]「But that's okay. Right now, I just want to be by Blue's side... And I want to take good care of the baby in my belly. That's all I need to be happy...」[k]
[テオ]「Riselle...」[k]
Do you think that much of Blue...?[k]
Once again, I realize that Riselle's heart no longer belongs to me.[k]
[textoff]
@out
@w05
@gameon
[texton w=0]
[マリア v=va166 f=08]「But if you stay here, you won't be able to give birth, let alone raise a child properly, will you?」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl402 e=マタニティドレス　 f=09]「That's...」[k]
[マリア v=va167 f=01]「Come to my house for now. There, you can raise your child without worrying about anyone else.」[k]
[リーゼル f=10]「...」[k]
[マリア v=va168 f=02]「I understand that you don't want to leave Blue, but right now you should take care of yourself and your baby. Why don't you leave this hideout for a while?」[k]
[リーゼル f=10]「...」[k]
[マリア v=va169 f=07]「I'm worried about you! Please understand.」[k]
[リーゼル f=10]「...」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl403 f=09]「...Okay. If you say so, Maria...」[k]
[マリア v=va170 f=03]「Great! Let's get going then! Your slave contract is no longer valid, so you can leave here immediately!」[k]
[リーゼル f=09]「...」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Riselle...」[k]
Riselle stands up and silently follows Maria. However, she looks somewhat unhappy.[k]
[テオ f=06]「Riselle...」[k]
Even though she accepted Maria's proposal, she still doesn't want to part with Blue...[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out
@w05

; サファイアシティ
@bg f=0005
@mu f=ending
[texton w=1]
Our party, accompanied by the rescued Riselle, arrived in front of Maria's apartment in Sapphire City.[k]
@fg c=マリア e=通常 f=02
[マリア v=va171 f=02]「Well then, you should stay here for a while.」[k]
[リーゼル v=vl404 f=01]「Thank you, Maria...」[k]
[マリア v=va172 f=05]「Hey, listen to me for a second.」[k]
Maria turns around and speaks to me.[k]
[テオ f=05]「What's wrong, Maria?」[k]
[マリア v=va173 f=06]「I'm thinking of leaving your party.」[k]
[マックス f=11]「Ehhhhh?!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「Why? Is it for Riselle's sake?」[k]
[マリア v=va174 f=14]「Yes... It's an important time before the birth, so someone has to take care of her, right?」[k]
[テオ f=06]「Yeah... Definitely.」[k]
[マリア v=va175 f=14]「After all, Riselle is a dear friend... I can't just leave her.」[k]
Maria said this with a very gentle look in her eyes.[k]
[マリア v=va176 f=02]「That's why I can't go with you guys...」[k]
[テオ f=02]「That's okay. You have your own priorities. Thank you so much for helping us until now.」[k]
[マックス f=19]「Hey, Maria, you don't have to leave the party. Please reconsider!」[k]
[マリア v=va177 f=07]「I've already made up my mind! I'm sorry, but give up.」[k]
[マックス f=19]「Oh no...」[k]
Max slumped his shoulders at Maria's cold response.[k]
[マリア v=va178 f=01]「Once Riselle has given birth safely and the child is able to take care of themselves, I might return to being an adventurer. After all, I do love adventuring!」[k]
[マックス f=03]「Hey! Come back to see us again when that happens!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「I'm looking forward to it. Take care of Riselle.」[k]
[マリア v=va179 f=01]「Everyone, keep up the good work! Well then, Riselle, let's go see the doctor first.」[k]
[リーゼル f=06]「... ∗nod∗」[k]
@cl
Riselle still looked uncertain, but she went with Maria without putting up much of a fight.[k]
I silently watched the two of them walk away.[k]
[マックス f=01]「Well then, let's go too.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Y-yeah.」[k]
I turned my back on Riselle and the others and started walking away.[k]
A woman who I once loved with all my heart. I dreamed of spending my future with her. But due to a twist of fate, it ended sadly.[k]
But I won't look back. I'm going to walk a new path.[k]
[textoff]
@fa
@out t=2000
@w2
