;■ミレディ加入

;◇イベント01・ミレディ加入
*miredy_1

; シーガルの村の酒場
@saveon
@bgf f=0012
@mu f=trick
@w05
[texton]
[テオ f=05]「Wait... That girl is...」[k]
[ミレディ e=通常 f=06]「...」[k]
When I visited the tavern in Seagull Village, I noticed a familiar face.[k]
She is a sylph girl named Miredy who was with Blue. She is sitting alone at a table in the tavern.
It's Miredy, the sylph who was with Blue. She's sitting alone at a table in the tavern.[k]
[ミレディ v=vm133 f=01]「Ah...!」[k]
Then Miredy spotted us and ran over to us.[k]
[textoff]
@fg c=ミレディ f=03
[texton w=1]
[ミレディ v=vm134 f=03]「Hey, long time no see～! How have you been～?」[k]
[テオ f=12]「A-ah...」[k]
Miredy spoke to me in a familiar manner. I was taken aback by her carefree attitude.[k]
@fg c=ミレディ f=02
[ミレディ v=vm135 f=02]「Hey, what are you guys doing right now?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「What do you mean? It's obvious, isn't it? We're traveling around as adventurers. We came here to eat.」[k]
[ミレディ v=vm136 f=01]「Wow, an adventure trip! That sounds great!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「You're an adventurer too, right? What's Blue's party up to now?」[k]
@fg c=ミレディ f=19
[ミレディ v=vm137 f=19]「I don't know.」[k]
[テオ f=05]「You don't know... Aren't you a member of Blue's party?」[k]
@fg c=ミレディ f=05
[ミレディ f=06]「...」[k]
[ミレディ v=vm138 f=05]「Blue kicked his party out...」[k]
[テオ f=12]「What?! Why?」[k]
@fg c=ミレディ f=19
[ミレディ v=vm139 f=19]「He said he didn't need me anymore. He said the reason he lost was because I was useless!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「O-oh...」[k]
@fg c=ミレディ f=51
[ミレディ v=vm140 f=51]「I helped him so much, but then he said he doesn't need me anymore. Isn't that horrible?」[k]
[テオ f=10]「I see... That's unfortunate...」[k]
I knew Blue was a cold person, but that's going too far... Doesn't he realize how useful her abilities are?[k]
@fg c=ミレディ f=02
[ミレディ v=vm141 f=02]「Hey, I have a favor to ask you.」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Huh? What is it?」[k]
[ミレディ v=vm142 f=01]「Take me along on your adventure too!」[k]
[テオ f=05]「So... you want to join our party?」[k]
@fgf c=ミレディ f=03
[ミレディ v=vm143 f=03]「Yes, yes!」[k]
; ↑ 期待を込めて嬉しそうに
[テオ f=10]「I don't know what to say...」[k]
[ミレディ v=vm144 f=01]「Like I said earlier, I got kicked out of Blue's party.」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
@fg c=ミレディ f=09
[ミレディ v=vm145 f=09]「So I have nowhere else to go. Please, take me with you!」[k]
[テオ f=10]「...」[k]
This girl has caused me so much suffering, and I still can't forgive her for taking Riselle away from me.[k]
...However, Blue is the real villain. Because she was involved with Blue, she became an accomplice to his crimes. In a sense, she may also be a victim of Blue, since she was abandoned as a result.[k]
Besides, I can't just leave a fragile girl like her out on the street. Can I really abandon her here?[k]
[テオ f=12]「...I guess it's okay for you to join.」[k]
@fgf c=ミレディ f=03
[ミレディ v=vm146 f=03]「Really? Awesome! You're so generous!」[k]
[テオ f=02]「Looking forward to working with you, Miredy.」[k]
[ミレディ v=vm147 f=04]「Let's have fun together～!」[k]
Maria left, after all, and things have been getting tough for the party. Her abilities will surely be useful.[k]
[textoff]
@st
@se f=up3
@notice text="<y>Miredy joined the party!"
@ws buf=2
@outf
